headline: Guggenheim Securities Hires Joel Fishbein to Expand Technology Investment Banking Practice
summary: NEW YORK, Aug. 07, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Guggenheim Securities, the investment banking and capital markets division of Guggenheim Partners, announced today that Joel Fishbein will join the firm’s Technology investment banking practice as a Senior Managing Director to focus on advising companies in the software sector. headline: ONEOK Prices $3B Senior Notes Offering to Refinance Debt
summary: ONEOK said proceeds will be used toward repaying its outstanding commercial paper and senior notes maturing Sept. 15.
